                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a creature the basilisk can see within 30 feet starts its turn, the basilisk can use its reaction to glance at the creature.</p>\n<p>The creature must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:20] save. If it fails, it gains the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} condition for 1 minute as its body slowly stiffens.</p>"
